        WHERE [s].[Name] = @__name_0 AND ([s].[TenantId] IS NULL) AND ([s].[UserId] IS NULL)) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END

VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, 0),
(@p7, @p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, 1),
(@p14, @p15, @p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, 2),
(@p21, @p22, @p23, @p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, 3)) AS i ([CreationTime], [CreatorUserId], [Discriminator], [IsGranted], [Name], [RoleId], [TenantId], _Position) ON 1=0
